elements.name: Como primer usuario inicio sesion y mandó un mensaje al usuario 2

steps.name: I send a signal to user 2 containing "login1 complete"
I wait for a signal containing "login2 complete" for 15 seconds
I click on the first conversation
I click on the redact message inputbox
I send a signal to user 2 containing "message1 sent"
I wait for a signal containing "message2 sent" for 15 seconds
